      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2be95153b7285f18",
      "text": "Economists point to the reduction of transaction costs in multipolar economic relations, sociologists stress the coordination advantages of resource pools, while lawyers tend to emphasize the legal \"immortality\" of non-corporeal entities-the immortality of the church, the state, the corporation. "
